{"tid":845230,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人人圍著我 無人明白我","createTime":"2018-10-02T13:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T13:30:45.000Z","uid":38907,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e03dcf2f9d90a9f12d630fb306e42313f494b6cf","tid":845230,"uid":38907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:20:18.000Z","msg":"外人睇 我好似好多圈子 好多朋友 生活多姿多彩 <br />\n但好多時其實我鐘意自己坐係公園聽下歌諗下嘢<br />\n但自己撫心自問 其實只係每個圈子都參一腳<br />\n圈子係好多 但好多都係圈子邊緣係咁重疊<br />\n就好似奧運個五個圈咁<br />\n可以我平時講嘢聲大大 又乜都9up一餐<br />\n人地覺得好好笑 好nice<br />\n甚至想認真做一樣嘢 人地都會覺得我玩玩下<br />\n有時好想搵人叫下春 但又唔知同邊個講 都唔知點講<br />\n<br />\n好似1999有冇人明個種寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2c0dc62dc4d4578577bc8fab09321e8767001c","tid":845230,"uid":1249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:21:37.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，我朋友都無啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2266cd1d6a26d5f4dc8f0069331678311b7bb46b","tid":845230,"uid":29820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:22:00.000Z","msg":"側田?"},{"pid":"52bc7db8ba81f103289fc0aefbfbd0d3bec32ddb","tid":845230,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"咁邊係人人圍住你呢<br />\n係你個個圈都入搏埋堆, 但係又做唔到核心分子"},{"pid":"11f1d674141f0ae1080262b3d45e4eb75dbfc1d2","tid":845230,"uid":38907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52bc7db8ba81f103289fc0aefbfbd0d3bec32ddb","tid":845230,"uid":41317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:23:33.000Z","msg":"咁邊係人人圍住你呢<br />\n係你個個圈都入搏埋堆, 但係又做唔到核心分子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:27:34.000Z","msg":"啲人成日話我去就去 <br />\n我唔去佢地又真係成班唔去<br />\n搞到我明明唔想去又好似好掃興咁<br />\n平時放咗工佢地約打邊爐 我唔想去 佢地又取消<br />\n中秋又係咁 我話唔出 佢地又話我唔出咁唔去<br />\n搞到好似比人逼去應酬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6238715d189aac96ffac2b176097f9fd3a9b76d","tid":845230,"uid":38907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2266cd1d6a26d5f4dc8f0069331678311b7bb46b","tid":845230,"uid":29820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:22:00.000Z","msg":"側田?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:30:11.000Z","msg":"泳兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34515ab3978013d8420b4e72a16b4f5eff2d72fe","tid":845230,"uid":38907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f2c0dc62dc4d4578577bc8fab09321e8767001c","tid":845230,"uid":1249,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:21:37.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，我朋友都無啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:30:45.000Z","msg":"瀟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}